</style><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>*由于此推文所附照片显示了每个人的脸部，因此我们已经处理了马赛克。</p></blockquote><p>有关Sayu发布的“Zaion LanZa文档”的详细信息，请参阅以下文章。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="H1Rps1sCC5"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-releases-documents-on-former-nijisanji-en-new-zaion-lanza/">VTuber Sayu 前NIJISANJI EN（新）在Lanza（Zaion LanZa）上发布文件</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Sayu 前 NIJISANJI EN（新）Lanza Zaion LanZa 文档已发布” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-releases-documents-on-former-nijisanji-en-new-zaion-lanza/embed/#?secret=qNTkYjltk0#?secret=H1Rps1sCC5" data-secret="H1Rps1sCC5" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="3o8cD1W2Zb"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-foreign-vtuber-listeners-and-fans-are-increasingly-critical-of-nijisanji-and-anycolor-in-response-to-the-contents-of-zaion-lanza-document/">部分海外VTuber观众和粉丝收到“Zaion LanZa文件” 加强对Nijisanji和ANYCOLOR的批评</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“一些海外VTuber观众/粉丝《Zaion LanZa文件》受到了对Nijisanji和ANYCOLOR的更强烈的批评” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-foreign-vtuber-listeners-and-fans-are-increasingly-critical-of-nijisanji-and-anycolor-in-response-to-the-contents-of-zaion-lanza-document/embed/#?secret=LvlBRvmqRD#?secret=3o8cD1W2Zb" data-secret="3o8cD1W2Zb" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> *本网站上的“NIJISANJI EN（新）”符号是为了区别于曾经存在的第一代“NIJISANJI EN（前NIJISANJI IN）”。</p></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ZaionLanZa" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zaion LanZa [NIJISANJI EN]</a> / <a href="https://twitter.com/ZaionLanZa" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zaion LanZa <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f643.png" alt="🙃" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ထNIJISANJI</a> / <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/talents/l/zaion-lanza" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">兰泽诗浓</a></p><cite>YouTube / Twitter / NIJISANJI EN（新）</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.anime-expo.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="动漫博览会">动漫博览会</a></p><cite>官方网站</cite></blockquote><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="yB0Cfkjdi6"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-actress-disclosed-zaion-lanza-document-receives-cheers-by-anime-expo/">VTuber Sayu的女演员（公开Zaion LanZa文件）受到Anime Expo的欢呼</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Sayu的女演员（公开Zaion LanZa文件）受到Anime Expo的欢呼” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-actress-disclosed-zaion-lanza-document-receives-cheers-by-anime-expo/embed/#?secret=qbEEk7ysul#?secret=yB0Cfkjdi6" data-secret="yB0Cfkjdi6" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-performer-and-voice-model-who-disclosed-zaion-lanza-document-receives-cheers-near-anime-expo-venue/">VTuber Sayu 的表演者/声优模特在动漫博览会会场附近受到欢呼“Zaion LanZa 文件”公众</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sayu-performer-and-voice-model-who-disulated-zaion-lanza-document-receives-cheers-near-anime-expo-venue/feed/ 0 95652
